{
  "ID": "GoR_MinnesotaTribe_Assassinate_NoWitnesses",
  "contractName": "No Witnesses",
  "contractDisplayStyle": "BaseCampaignNormal",
  "difficulty": 8,
  "difficultyUIModifier": 0,
  "weight": 1,
  "scope": "STANDARD",
  "finalDifficulty": 0,
  "shortDescription": "<b>Star Captain Elias Jorgensson</b> of [[DM.Factions[faction_GhostBearWatch],Ghost Bear Watch]] has conducted extensive surveillance operations within [[DM.Factions[faction_MinnesotaTribe],Tribe]] territory over the past three months. Intelligence confirms he has mapped our network structure, identified key personnel, and documented operational patterns that could compromise our entire cell organization if transmitted to Ghost Bear command.\n\nJorgensson is currently on <i>Niops</i>, conducting final intelligence gathering before evacuation. Our window to neutralize this threat is narrow. Once he realizes he's been compromised, contingency protocols will activate and he will attempt immediate evacuation from the system.\n\nYou are to locate and eliminate the target in the urban sector before he can reach his evacuation point. Expected opposition includes Jorgensson's advanced mech plus escort lance providing security.\n\nOperational security is paramount. Jorgensson possesses intelligence that exposes our entire regional network. He cannot be allowed to reach Ghost Bear Watch command.",
  "longDescription": "Boss, this guy knows too much about Tribe operations. If he reaches Ghost Bear command with what he's got, Joanna's entire network burns. We stop him here or we don't stop him at all.",
  "salvagePotential": 16,
